<h3 id="money">
<a class="heading-anchor" href="#money" hidden><svg width="16" height="16"><use xlink:href="https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#anchor"></use></svg></a>Money <a href="https://flathub.org/apps/details/org.nickvision.money"><svg width='16' height='16'><use xlink:href='https://thisweek.gnome.org/images/icons.svg#link'></use></svg></a>
</h3><p>A personal finance manager.</p>
<p><a href="https://matrix.to/#/@nlogozzo:matrix.org">Nick</a> reports</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Money <a href="https://github.com/nlogozzo/NickvisionMoney/releases/tag/2023.1.0-beta3">V2023.1.0-beta3</a> is here! This beta features a brand new repeat transactions system (with support for biweekly transactions), as well as some design tweaks and performance improvements.</p>
<p><a href="https://hosted.weblate.org/engage/nickvision-money/">Money is also now available to translate on Weblate!</a> We welcome all users to come and translate Money is their language :)</p>
<p>Continued thanks to all the developers, testers, and translations (especially Fyodor Sobolev) for all their hard work as we gear up for the stable release next week!</p>
